flowRoot.flowPara: Generate structured search queries. Extract city names, meta-data and thematic content of articles using computer assisted tools. Identify and address gaps.
Develop research questions with stakeholders. Perform focused reviews by topic and case using systematic methods for literature selection.
Aim: strengthen single and low-n case study research by assessing multiple inter-linked issues
Limitations: difficult to generalise; few cities with adequate literature; limited opportunity to apply formal methods
Aim: identify the contextual factors and drivers of variation in outcomes between cities
Limitations: important cases potentially missing; cannot capture full scope of inter-linked issues
